These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, german, australian, argentine, japanese, turkish, chinese
1. the german is in the middle##1
2. the german is on the left of the australian##1
3. the japanese is on the right of the argentine##1
4. the pakistani is on the right of the australian##1
5. the chinese is on the far left##1
6. the turkish is on the right of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | chinese | argentine | japanese | german | australian | pakistani | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  social-worker, pilot, dressmaker, security-guard, bartender, software-developer, videographer
1. the videographer is on the far right##1
2. the social-worker is on the far left##1
3. the social-worker is on the left of the bartender##1
4. the bartender is on the left of the dressmaker##1
5. the security-guard is on the right of the software-developer##1
6. the videographer is on the right of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | social-worker | bartender | dressmaker | software-developer | security-guard | pilot | videographer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, cooking, skydiving, gardening, baking, reading, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | baking | singing | reading | skydiving | hiking | cooking | gardening |

 #################################

 
