.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: romance, time-travel, documentary, western, spy, zombie, musical
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | time-travel | romance | zombie | western | musical | documentary |

